data.description: WELCOME TO YOUR COZY HOME AT THE SOUGHT INSPIRADA COMMUNITY. NESTLED IN A QUIET NEIGHBORHOOD, THIS ADORABLE 2 STORY, 3 BEDROOM, 3 BA,  2 CAR GARAGE IS A CONTEMPORARY HOME THAT SITS ON A CORNER LOT.  FEATURING 1,696 SQ FT OF CHARM.  A SPACIOUS LIVING ROOM WITH FRESH PAINT AND UPGRADED WATERPROOF FLOORING WITH A SEPARATE DINING AREA THAT HAS CUSTOM LIGHTING.  THE KITCHEN FEATURES NEW GRANITE COUNTER TOPS AND STAINLESS STEEL APPLIANCES WITH AN EXTRA LARGE WALK-IN PANTRY.  SEPARATE LAUNDRY ROOM, THE MASTER BEDROOM HAS A LARGE WALK-IN CLOSET AND THE MASTER BATH HAS A SEPARATE SHOWER/TUB.  THE COMMUNITY CLUBHOUSE FEATURES A POOL AND COMMUNITY PARK.  CLOSE TO SHOPPING, DINING AND ENTERTAINMENT.
